This page is copied from the [https://web.archive.org/web/https://www.coactivate.org/projects/disintermedia/project-home archived project home page] of [[Disintermedia]], as the original platform went away and may not reappear. Some of the pages of particular interest to us, in terms of the Commons and P2P, are reproduced (and may be maintained) on this wiki. These are listed on the general [[Disintermedia]] page. 

